My good friends @biggsharley gave me the opportunity to take this beautiful FXLRST in White Sand Pearl out for a spin the other day. WOW!! Is all I can say about this color and this bike. Such a fun one to rip around on. It’s light and nimble yet has great wind protection and plenty of storage. It like a baby bagger with really big power right off the showroom floor. A couple small mods and this bike is ready for whatever you throw at it weather it’s ripping the canyons or taking a long road trip. 
•
Go see my boy @jhubb23 over @biggsharley to get a test ride today.
